      <h2>Home Organising</h2>
      <p>Set up easy systems for everyday life. Think baskets, labels, and storage that actually fits your routines. I'll create a layout that's simple to maintain, whether you're a family of five or living solo.</p>
      <p><a class="link" href="/contact">Let's organise it</a></p>
